Follow these steps to check this and fix it: 

1. Open the Charms bar and click or tap on Search.

2. Enter "advanced sharing" in the search box, and then click

or tap on Change advanced sharing settings.

3. Click or tap on Private network profile to expand the list.

4. Next, click or tap on Turn on network discovery in case it is

turned off.

5. Now just confirm this change by clicking or tapping on Save

changes.